data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! SELLER OFFERING UP TO $10,000 IN CLOSING COSTS. ROOF TO BE REPLACED WITH ACCEPTED OFFER. Pool home in the heart of Niceville. Brick and vinyl home with 3 bedroom 2 bathroom has tile and LVP throughout the main living areas. Carpet in the bedrooms. Spacious kitchen and dining area with breakfast bar. Open the patio door to a covered deck and head down the stairs to an oversize screened pool with slide and separate jacuzzi. On those cool nights come in from the jacuzzi and turn on your gas fireplace. Workshop in the back has electricity.
